{
  "stem": "18813.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] If you didn't give-- so you know that there's no tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe they had warning, but you, you couldn't imagine that something like it would happen, for no reason that somebody would come to you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was in the business 30 years, or whatever-- that that would be taken away in the second without any warnings, nothing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it's-- nobody-- nobody expected that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that-- just a moment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have to think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After that was-- I was going for a while to the business and coming home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were still living, I don't know, a month or two in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And next to Cracow in the mountains, they open a camp, Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, it was a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm sorry, it was ghetto before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that was not far from Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we moved to the-- we moved-- we had to move to ghetto with another one-- two-bedroom apartment with another two families, one on the top of the other.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we made the best out of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there I got the job on the airport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So that wasn't too bad because I was never hungry there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Planes were coming and leaving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had to clean the office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that German was very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was giving me to eat, you know, giving me a piece of bread, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So that was good then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And at night, the trucks were taking us back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But after a while, they liquidated the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The came and took us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, just went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe-- I'm sorry to interrupt you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe we had a little package in the end, every one of us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I really don't remember how big the package was or what was in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
